messages.message: I tried the Identity Verification app. It only provides very basic information about each. This is not very impressive. It doesn't return dates, ID number, DOBs, etc.
@ChrisM can you help us understand what type of document it was?

It was one of the passport sample documents provided in the app. I struggle to see the value in an app with so little data. And, like my other post, we need to be able to edit in human review or these are not useful apps.
this seems like a bug that we are tracking. the results in the screenshot seem to have fun the doc summary app on the identity verification documents. this bug is fixed in dev

that being said, even the actual identity verification app only has a few p0 fields (more than this, but less than traditional ib solutions) for now and no human review capability. we will improve its quality post launch based on customer demand, and human review will come with enterprise builder. cc: @Bastiane
